comment: /**  * Return the file {@link Kind} (added, modified, deleted).  * @return the kind  */
code: /**  * Return the file {@link Kind} (added, modified, deleted).  * @return the kind  */ public Kind getKind() {     return this.kind. }

code: /**  * Return the time that the file was last modified.  * @return the last modified time  */ public long getLastModified() {     return this.lastModified. }

code: /**  * Return the contents of the file as a byte array or {@code null} if  * {@link #getKind()} is {@link Kind#DELETED}.  * @return the contents or {@code null}  */ public byte[] getContents() {     return this.contents. }
